descriptionShort: Tracker for cryptocurrencies market cap, ranking and price.
title: CoinSky

creator: Coinsky
descriptionHtml:
CoinSky is a cryptocurrency tracker and blockchain market analysis tool. We provide accurate, comprehensive and effective cryptocurrency information in real time, from cryptocurrency tracker, price alerts, gas alerts to various convenient investment advice, aiming to escort your digital asset management.

1. Track real-time cryptocurrency data, more than 9000 cryptocurrencies including BTC, ETH, BNB, USDC, etc. ;
2. Monitor & alert gas abnormality and track the fluctuation of gas fees on major chains;
3. Continuously update newly-listed coins on the exchanges to help you grasp every investment opportunity ;
4. Integrate wealth management products from main exchanges to help you control investment risks;
5. Provide various useful tools for Crypto Converter, Authorized Wallets and Cryptocurrency 101;

Track the data of Over 9000 Cryptocurrencies
Based on the data from major chains and exchanges, CoinSky tracks real-time cryptocurrencies data, and rank your favorite cryptocurrencies in four dimensions covering market value, trading volume, current price, and price fluctuation. The K-line chart represents the price moves of a crypto for a given timeframe, enabling you to pick profitable coins . For more cryptocurrency information, you can click the links to the official websites, communities, etc. for details.

Price alerts
Gas fee alerts: Real-time monitoring of the fluctuation of gas fees on main chains such as Ethereum, and trace the source of abnormal transaction events and contracts. Equip you with insight into the market trends, and keep up with every investment opportunity, no more FOMO.

Cryptocurrency price alerts: Add the crypto(s) you care about to the watchlist, and set the price reminder for each. Once the price of the crypto(s) you marked falls or rises to the warning line you set, we will notify you in time , and you will never miss each trading opportunity.

Access all investment opportunities with one click
New listings on exchanges: real-time updates and forecasts of the latest currencies listed on major exchanges such as Binance, coinbase, FTX, Okx, etc. Help you grasp the most comprehensive information such as listing time and price, and find potential coins. Invest faster and get rich faster.

Stable Earning: Collect financial management projects of main exchanges such as Binance and OKX. The APY and lock-up period are clear at a glance, and you will no longer have to switch back and forth between multiple apps. CoinSky helps you do the first step of rational investment.

Asset Escort and Wallet Protection
Authorized Wallets: this feature can check the details of your authorized contracts, and then cancel unsafe or expired authorized contracts in time to ensure wallet security and asset security.

Various tools that are easy to use
Cryptocurrency and Fiat Currency Converter: Provide exchange rate conversion between various cryptocurrencies and fiat currencies including ETH, BTC, BNB, USD, allowing you to calculate profits in one second, and improve the efficiency of investment decision-making.

Beginner’s Class: Newbie's introductory book, which systematically introduces the basic concepts and knowledge of blockchain. You’ll learn about the rise and fall logic of cryptocurrencies, understand current popular projects and project logic. Now start to learn and grasp investment opportunities.


If you are interested in NFT, we will also have fun functions such as NFT regeneration, so stay tuned!

We will continue to update features to escort your crypto investment and enrich your crypto journey.

Grasp the most comprehensive cryptocurrency information. All handy tools on one small-size app.

All at CoinSky.

creator: Coinsky
descriptionHtml:
CoinSky is a comprehensive Web3 blockchain APP.

CoinSky provides the latest cryptocurrency market data, and the most prompt & accurate market news so that you can have more initiatives to grasp the whole picture of the market.

Powerful Web3 Features:
➢ Trade cryptocurrencies such as BTC, ETH, USDC, and USDT.
➢ Track real-time market data for thousands of cryptocurrencies including BTC, ETH, BNB, and USDC.
➢ Monitor Ethereum gas fee, track and alert on gas anomalies.
➢ Use NFT Creator to create your own Bored Ape For Everyone NFT with a click.
➢ Integrate financial products from major exchanges for more investment opportunities.
➢ Keep track of Twitter trends to help you make better investment decisions.
➢ Provide various web3 tools such as cryptocurrency conversion, wallet security check, and smart contract scan.

#Cryptos Market
CoinSky tracks cryptocurrency prices and trends in real time, following data from major blockchains and exchanges. It can also rank cryptocurrencies in four dimensions: market cap, trading volume, up/down, and price, making it easy to find investment opportunities in cryptocurrencies.

#New Coins Listing
CoinSky provides live updates on the latest coins and tokens listed on major exchanges such as Binance, which helps you to have the most comprehensive information such as listing times, prices, ups & downs, and discover potential crypto coins and tokens.

#Price Alert
Add your favorite cryptocurrencies to the list below and turn on price alerts for each one. We will notify you in real time when the price of your subscribed cryptocurrency drops or rises to an alert line, so you will no longer miss any trading opportunities.

#Gas Tracker
Monitor fluctuations in gas fees on popular blockchains such as Ethereum in real time and track the source of unusual trading events and contracts. Empowering you with insight into market trends and keeping up with every investment opportunity, there will be no more FOMO.

#NFT Creator
In CoinSky, you can easily create your own Bored Ape For Everyone NFT without paying the gas fee. NFT can be sold in OpenSea and thereby earn your first crypto income.

All forms of investment come with risk, including the risk of losing the entire amount of the investment. It may not be ideal for everyone.
